                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18291029-227-off1286 t18291029-227-cd1287"></join>, at Christchurch, 2 silver watches, value 6l.; 1 seal, value 10s., and 1 gold ring, value 2l., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18291029-227-victim1877" type="victimName">
